comments: Mills (SAS) exits the paint within three seconds.
Mills (SAS) jumps vertically and absorbs the ensuing body contact with Doncic (DAL) following the release of the ball.  The contact is considered incidental.
Doncic (DAL) makes incidental contact with Carroll (SAS) during the rebound.
Carroll (SAS) makes marginal contact with Curry (DAL) as he attempts to gather the ball.
Aldridge (SAS) reaches in and makes contact with the ball during Porzingis's (DAL) upward shooting motion.
Aldridge (SAS) extends his hip into Curry's (DAL) path and delivers contact during the screen.
Kleber (DAL) cleanly deflects the pass intended for DeRozan (SAS).
Forbes (SAS) makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm that affects his ability to gather the ball during his drive.
Doncic (DAL) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Aldridge's (SAS) arm that does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Aldridge (SAS) makes marginal contact with Porzingis (DAL) during the pick and allows him to contest the jump shot attempt by Gay (SAS).
Porzingis (DAL) grabs and pulls Aldridge's (SAS) jersey.
Forbes (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position during Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Gay (SAS) fails to inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
DeRozan (SAS) makes marginal contact with Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter that does not affect his SQBR.
Doncic (DAL) dribbles the ball off of Forbes's (SAS) foot and he does not intentionally kick it.
Doncic (DAL) and DeRozan (SAS) make incidental contact with each other attempting to retrieve the loose ball.
After Doncic (DAL) recovers the loose ball, Gay (SAS) reaches in and makes contact with the ball.
Aldridge (SAS) reaches in and makes contact with the ball during Doncic's (DAL) attempt to pass. The contact following the deflection is deemed incidental.
